{"tid":2344591,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"公園新星-失業毒男大揭秘：28歲單身男人工3萬！每月只用3千！其餘錢投資＋定期＋保險","createTime":"2020-12-29T00:50:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T07:08:46.000Z","uid":71166,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c54276c2153ae1fbc18c1caa123148b802fea486","tid":2344591,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T00:50:38.000Z","msg":"28歲單身男人工有3萬元，每月使費只用3千元！其餘錢全新用作投資，包括月供股票、定期存款、供保險，餘錢會全部儲起來等待投資時機及備用！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.businesstimes.com.hk/data/thumbs/full/116140/750/0/0/0/28-3-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.businesstimes.com.hk%2Fdata%2Fthumbs%2Ffull%2F116140%2F750%2F0%2F0%2F0%2F28-3-3.jpg&h=701eb178&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2a1bc5a5a6f0c992f443eda7eb1e58670f36ce8","tid":2344591,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T00:51:01.000Z","msg":"理財個案｜讀者來信：28歲單身男人工3萬 每月只用3千 <br />\n成Sir 你好，我今年28歲單身，人工每月$30,000，每個月會用$7,000放入月供股票，分別是：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://02800.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02800.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=f64450e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02800.HK</a> @ $3,000<br />\n<a href=\"http://00027.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00027.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=84c8e997\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00027.HK</a> @ $2,000<br />\n<a href=\"http://00006.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00006.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=10b57518\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00006.HK</a> @ $2,000"},{"pid":"655518c3292a91ad550c8455aa8db726c2e62d24","tid":2344591,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T00:51:26.000Z","msg":"有定期存款 ＋ 保險<br />\n月供股票現時儲咗大約 $125,000。另外每個月$6,000會放入定期，年利率約3%，定期現儲共有約$140,000，現可隨時拎錢，停供或減少供款。每月大約$3,000供保險，扣除其他費用有$11,000其餘會儲起來等待投資時機及備用。"},{"pid":"3a8b20fd3af84cbbef228a60412ca6136f2cdfd2","tid":2344591,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T00:51:46.000Z","msg":"另外我有以下股份<br />\n股票代號 數量 買入價<br />\n<a href=\"http://09988.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F09988.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=e22bd0c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">09988.HK</a> 5手 178<br />\n<a href=\"http://02128.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02128.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=fff83889\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02128.HK</a> 5手 10.2<br />\n<a href=\"http://01928.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01928.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=94d1a009\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01928.HK</a> 4手 30.65<br />\n<a href=\"http://00241.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00241.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=f5fa1353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00241.HK</a> 2手 19.86<br />\n<a href=\"http://03319.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F03319.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=3415f43b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">03319.HK</a> 5手 39.9"},{"pid":"c91c3aa38e52ae00679e131559d5176791c0b99f","tid":2344591,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T00:52:03.000Z","msg":"以上5隻股票現總值約$385,000<br />\n扣除股票，現有流動資金約$500,000（連埋定期）， 無其他資產"},{"pid":"88909a64fae4d3ae370edb2d505f5349a2220e29","tid":2344591,"uid":196924,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T00:52:12.000Z","msg":"每月使費3千蚊即係住老母食老母但係唔俾家用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6bfa71b5262846b0a0e760af7b8a52558467e2","tid":2344591,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T00:52:20.000Z","msg":"要更改投資組合嗎？ <br />\n我現在的月供股票中， 以我現時情況我需要更改投資組合嗎， 另外（<a href=\"http://00006.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00006.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=10b57518\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00006.HK</a>） 很像沒什麼升值力， 我需要停供嗎？<br />\n我另外持有的5隻股票中， 質素前景如何呢？可持有嗎？ 而（<a href=\"http://09988.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F09988.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=e22bd0c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">09988.HK</a>） 同（<a href=\"http://00241.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00241.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=f5fa1353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00241.HK</a>） 都係阿里系， 這個比例會太高風險嗎？<br />\n我現時月供股票連同其他股票佔我的總資產約50%， 比例有冇需要增加減少。 餘下的$500,000可以如何再投資<br />\n我一年保險費佔我人工1/12, 這個比例算唔算合理唔該！"},{"pid":"b466d5b09687014b11d175ac3526081fc6207ef5","tid":2344591,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T00:52:31.000Z","msg":"月供2800<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbfdfdd14fb5e32317b4624cbd353b7faec2da8","tid":2344591,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T00:52:53.000Z","msg":"龔成老師分析：轉買較有增長力的股票 <br />\n1）你的年齡，應該進取少少，你可以轉一隻，改為較有增長力的股票。可考慮：華夏恆生科技ETF（<a href=\"http://03088.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F03088.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=61c8cc27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">03088.HK</a>）、阿里（<a href=\"http://09988.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F09988.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=e22bd0c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">09988.HK</a>）、騰訊（<a href=\"http://00700.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00700.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=bb162775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00700.HK</a>）、港交所（<a href=\"http://00388.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00388.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=0522e3cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00388.HK</a>）、舜宇光學（<a href=\"http://02382.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F02382.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=6a39911d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">02382.HK</a>）、小米（<a href=\"http://01810.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01810.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=ee983596\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01810.HK</a>）、比亞迪（<a href=\"http://01211.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01211.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=8932d747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01211.HK</a>）、中生製藥（<a href=\"http://01177.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01177.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=f9a58435\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01177.HK</a>）。<br />\n<br />\n2）都不差，但阿里健康（<a href=\"http://00241.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00241.HK&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=f5fa1353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00241.HK</a>）風險度較高，唔建議持有太多。業務上，有好大的潛力，不過，本質波動，股價上落大，消息多，市場炒作多，這類股風險都不少。最大問題是無人能正確估值，市場現時只是估估下，推將唔到佢將來的價值。這類股只建議小注持有，唔好加注，原有貨，如果你本身目標是長線，繼續持有無問題，但你預佢股價上落大。"},{"pid":"1333db9071a826683e4773484ddba6fa5c6d4b20","tid":2344591,"uid":42734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T00:53:04.000Z","msg":"以你的年齡，可以承受更多風險。建議投注小注潛力股，如1177、1830，其餘大部分投資有價值的股票，如2800、0014&hellip;snnfjfnsnsid慢慢讓資金自己滾存"},{"pid":"ad6a86400ccec85aa785123d0627f31b976e050f","tid":2344591,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T00:53:16.000Z","msg":"預持有3至5成現金<br />\n3）現時的大市平貴，你預持有3-5成現金是可以的。現時大市處合理區，可以一邊投資一邊留現金，而餘下現金的運用，就是等大跌市時出手。<br />\n<br />\n4）無絕對的，每個人不同。你比例可以的。"},{"pid":"cb7ecf13259d1a776a836d7a414c41fcead8b35d","tid":2344591,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad6a86400ccec85aa785123d0627f31b976e050f","tid":2344591,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"re